  "description": "<i>Hai no Majutsushi</i> is an implementation of Mahjong tile game. The opponents in the game are characters from <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/search/quick?company=Konami\">Konami</a>'s popular franchises: Simon Belmont from <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/search/quick?game=Castlevania+series\">Castlevania</a> series, Aphrodite and Poporon (Popolon) from <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/search/quick?game=Knightmare\">Knightmare</a> series, a snatcher from <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/game/snatcher\">Snatcher</a>, Dr. Venom from <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/search/quick?game=Gradius+series\">Gradius</a> series, Goemon from <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/search/quick?game=Ganbare+Goemon+series\">Ganbare Goemon</a> series, Penta the penguin from <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/search/quick?game=Antarctic+Adventure+series\">Antarctic Adventure</a> series, and Moai from <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/search/quick?game=Gradius+series\">Gradius</a> / <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/search/quick?game=Parodius\">Parodius</a> series.",
